**RESOURCE METHODS**

**GET**

There is two types of service offered by GET

- GET based on id: It returns &quot;postmessage&quot; based on id.
- GET based on all List: It returns all the available &quot;postmessage&quot;.

**Example of a request**

GET api/postmessage/getall

ACCEPT: application/json

$ curl [http://ec2-34-228-26-63.compute-1.amazonaws.com/api/postmessage/getall](http://ec2-34-228-26-63.compute-1.amazonaws.com/api/postmessage/getall)

**Response:**

[{&quot;id&quot;:2,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;message1&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;content1&quot;,&quot;addtime&quot;:1489825793,&quot;user\_id&quot;:1},{&quot;id&quot;:4,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;message3&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;content3&quot;,&quot;addtime&quot;:1489825793,&quot;user\_id&quot;:1},{&quot;id&quot;:11,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;sadsadasd&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;sadsadsad&quot;,&quot;addtime&quot;:null,&quot;user\_id&quot;:1},{&quot;id&quot;:12,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;dsfdsfs&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;sadfdsafdfdsfdsf&quot;,&quot;addtime&quot;:null,&quot;user\_id&quot;:1},{&quot;id&quot;:17,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;test&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;test&quot;,&quot;addtime&quot;:null,&quot;user\_id&quot;:1},{&quot;id&quot;:19,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;madam&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;sadasdsad&quot;,&quot;addtime&quot;:null,&quot;user\_id&quot;:1}

**POST**

Post creates a new entry, i.e. &quot;postmessage&quot;.

**Example of a request**

POST api/postmessage/

RawInput : {&quot;title&quot;:&quot;test&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;test&quot;}

Response:

{&quot;postId&quot;:&quot;25&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;test&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;test&quot;,&quot;addtime&quot;:null,&quot;userId&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}

**DELETE**

Delete lets you delete the &quot;postmessage&quot; based on the given id.

**Example of a request**

DELETE: [/api/postmessage/delete/2](http://ec2-34-228-26-63.compute-1.amazonaws.com/api/postmessage/delete/2)

ACCEPT: application/json

**Response:**

[{&quot;id&quot;:2,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;message1&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;content1&quot;,&quot;addtime&quot;:1489825793,&quot;user\_id&quot;:1,&quot;palindrom&quot;:0}]
